{"type":"message","id":"a0e0fac1","parentId":"516c7d43","timestamp":"2026-03-14T08:53:28.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户只是打了个招呼\"你好\"。这是一个简单的问候，我应该友好地回应，同时也可以提醒之前未完成的对话（关于那张图片的识别问题）。\n\n不过用户可能只是简单地打招呼，我不应该过度追问之前的事情，但可以友好地问候并询问有什么可以帮助的。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773478403362}}
