{"type":"message","id":"1c8b6ba5","parentId":"7ece85c0","timestamp":"2026-03-14T09:14:54.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想让我检查电脑上是否安装了QQ，如果没有就帮忙安装。我需要：\n\n1. 先检查QQ是否已经安装\n2. 如果没有安装，帮助用户安装\n\n让我先执行命令检查QQ是否安装。在Windows上，我可以检查常见的安装路径，或者使用命令查找。\n\n常见的QQ安装路径：\n- C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Tencent\\QQ\n- C:\\Program Files\\Tencent\\QQ\n- %USERPROFILE%\\AppData\\Local\\Tencent\\QQ\n\n或者通过注册表或开始菜单查找。\n\n让我先执行命令检查。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你检查电脑上是否安装了QQ。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Test-Path \"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Tencent\\QQ\\Bin\\QQ.exe\"; Test-Path \"$env:USERPROFILE\\AppData\\Local\\Tencent\\QQ\\Bin\\QQ.exe\"; Get-ItemProperty HKLM:\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\* | Where-Object { $_.DisplayName -like \"*QQ*\" } | Select-Object DisplayName, DisplayVersion"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773479677566}}
