{"type":"message","id":"856f4ce6","parentId":"cb0a8881","timestamp":"2026-03-14T09:15:03.701Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"检查结果显示没有找到QQ的安装路径，说明QQ当前没有安装在你的电脑上。\n\n现在我需要帮用户安装QQ。有几种方式可以安装QQ：\n1. 通过Microsoft Store安装（如果可用）\n2. 从腾讯官网下载安装包\n3. 使用winget（Windows包管理器）\n\n我先检查是否有winget可用，这是最简单的方式。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"检查结果显示，你的电脑上**没有安装QQ**。\n\n我来帮你安装。我尝试使用Windows包管理器（winget）来安装："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"winget install --id Tencent.QQ --silent --accept-package-agreements --accept-source-agreements","timeout":180}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773479695734}}
