{"type":"message","id":"fad2761f","parentId":"2f659cbb","timestamp":"2026-03-14T09:29:53.743Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"QQ官方下载链接失效了，让我尝试使用winget的另一个版本或者其他方法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:19","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 尝试使用winget安装一个较旧的稳定版本\nWrite-Host \"尝试安装 QQ 9.7.23...\"\nwinget install --id Tencent.QQ --version 9.7.23.29392 --exact --silent --accept-package-agreements --accept-source-agreements --disable-interactivity --override \"/S\" 2>&1\n\nWrite-Host \"---\"\nWrite-Host \"检查安装结果...\"\n$qqPaths = @(\n    \"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Tencent\\QQ\\Bin\\QQ.exe\",\n    \"C:\\Program Files\\Tencent\\QQ\\Bin\\QQ.exe\",\n    \"$env:USERPROFILE\\AppData\\Local\\Tencent\\QQ\\Bin\\QQ.exe\"\n)\n$found = $false\nforeach ($path in $qqPaths) {\n    if (Test-Path $path) {\n        Write-Host \"✅ 找到QQ: $path\"\n        $found = $true\n        break\n    }\n}\nif (-not $found) {\n    Write-Host \"❌ 未找到QQ安装\"\n}\n\n# 检查winget列表\nWrite-Host \"---\"\nWrite-Host \"winget列表中的QQ:\"\nwinget list --id Tencent.QQ 2>&1 | Select-String -Pattern \"QQ\"","timeout":300}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773480562120}}
