{"type":"message","id":"c7697b13","parentId":"fc6e0b17","timestamp":"2026-03-14T17:42:28.105Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"process:30","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"���Դ� https://dldir1v6.qq.com/qqfile/qq/QQNT/Windows/QQ_9.9.15_240808_x64_01.exe ����QQ...\n? ���سɹ����ļ���С: 188.31 MB\n\n��ʼ��װQQ...\n��װ�����������У������ĵȴ�...\n\n? ��װ�����г��ִ���: This command cannot be run due to the error: An error occurred trying to start process 'C:\\Users\\LWS\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\QQ_Installer.exe' with working directory 'C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace'. �����ѱ��û�ȡ����\n\n��������ʱ��װ��"}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"salty-canyon","total":9,"totalLines":9,"totalChars":415,"truncated":false,"exitCode":0,"name":"# 清理之前的临时文件"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773510148103}}
{"type":"message","id":"3abe3b12","parentId":"c7697b13","timestamp":"2026-03-14T17:42:28.107Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"process:31","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"salty-canyon completed 2m22s :: # 清理之前的临时文件"}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessions":[{"sessionId":"salty-canyon","status":"completed","startedAt":1773509938703,"endedAt":1773510080640,"runtimeMs":141937,"cwd":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace","command":"# 清理之前的临时文件\nRemove-Item -Path \"$env:TEMP\\QQ*\" -Recurse -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n# 使用另一个QQ下载链接 (QQ官网)\n$downloadUrls = @(\n    \"https://dldir1v6.qq.com/qqfile/qq/QQNT/Windows/QQ_9.9.15_240808_x64_01.exe\",\n    \"https://dldir1v6.qq.com/qqfile/qq/PCQQ9.7.23/QQ9.7.23.29392.exe\",\n    \"https://im.qq.com/pcqq\"\n)\n\n$outputPath = \"$env:TEMP\\QQ_Installer.exe\"\n$success = $false\n\nforeach ($url in $downloadUrls[0..1]) {\n    Write-Host \"尝试从 $url 下载QQ...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    try {\n        Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $url -OutFile $outputPath -UseBasicParsing -MaximumRedirection 5 -TimeoutSec 120\n        \n        if (Test-Path $outputPath) {\n            $fileSize = (Get-Item $outputPath).Length\n            if ($fileSize -gt 10MB) {\n                Write-Host \"✅ 下载成功！文件大小: $([math]::Round($fileSize / 1MB, 2)) MB\" -ForegroundColor Green\n                $success = $true\n                break\n            } else {\n                Write-Host \"⚠️ 文件太小，可能下载不完整，尝试下一个链接...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n                Remove-Item -Path $outputPath -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            }\n        }\n    } catch {\n        Write-Host \"❌ 下载失败: $_\" -ForegroundColor Red\n        Remove-Item -Path $outputPath -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    }\n}\n\nif (-not $success) {\n    Write-Host \"❌ 所有下载链接都失败了，请手动下载QQ安装包\" -ForegroundColor Red\n    Write-Host \"你可以访问 https://im.qq.com 手动下载安装\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# 开始安装\nWrite-Host \"`n开始安装QQ...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\nWrite-Host \"安装程序正在运行，请耐心等待...\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n\ntry {\n    # 启动安装程序\n    $process = Start-Process -FilePath $outputPath -ArgumentList \"/S\", \"/D=C:\\Program Files\\Tencent\\QQ\" -PassThru -Wait\n    \n    # 等待安装完成\n    Start-Sleep -Seconds 10\n    \n    # 检查安装结果\n    $qqPaths = @(\n        \"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Tencent\\QQ\\Bin\\QQ.exe\",\n        \"C:\\Program Files\\Tencent\\QQ\\Bin\\QQ.exe\",\n        \"C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Tencent\\QQ\\QQ.exe\",\n        \"C:\\Program Files\\Tencent\\QQ\\QQ.exe\"\n    )\n    \n    $found = $false\n    foreach ($path in $qqPaths) {\n        if (Test-Path $path) {\n            Write-Host \"`n✅ QQ安装成功！\" -ForegroundColor Green\n            Write-Host \"安装路径: $path\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n            $found = $true\n            break\n        }\n    }\n    \n    if (-not $found) {\n        Write-Host \"`n⚠️ 安装程序已运行，但无法确认安装位置\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n        Write-Host \"请检查开始菜单或桌面是否有QQ图标\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Host \"`n❌ 安装过程中出现错误: $_\" -ForegroundColor Red\n} finally {\n    # 清理安装包\n    if (Test-Path $outputPath) {\n        Remove-Item -Path $outputPath -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        Write-Host \"`n已清理临时安装包\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n    }\n}","name":"# 清理之前的临时文件","tail":"���Դ� https://dldir1v6.qq.com/qqfile/qq/QQNT/Windows/QQ_9.9.15_240808_x64_01.exe ����QQ...\r\n? ���سɹ����ļ���С: 188.31 MB\r\n\n��ʼ��װQQ...\r\n��װ�����������У������ĵȴ�...\r\n\n? ��װ�����г��ִ���: This command cannot be run due to the error: An error occurred trying to start process 'C:\\Users\\LWS\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\QQ_Installer.exe' with working directory 'C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace'. �����ѱ��û�ȡ����\r\n\n��������ʱ��װ��\r\n","truncated":false,"exitCode":0}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773510148103}}
{"type":"message","id":"d15fabd7","parentId":"3abe3b12","timestamp":"2026-03-14T17:42:48.453Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据日志显示，QQ安装失败的原因是：**安装包下载成功了（188.31MB），但在启动安装程序时出错**。\n\n错误信息显示：\n```\nThis command cannot be run due to the error: An error occurred trying to start process 'C:\\Users\\LWS\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\QQ_Installer.exe' with working directory 'C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace'. �����ѱ��û�ȡ����\n```\n\n看起来可能是：\n1. 安装程序被系统拦截了\n2. 需要用户确认/管理员权限\n3. 或者安装包有问题\n\n我需要：\n1. 先告诉用户QQ安装失败的情况\n2. 提供手动下载安装的方案（因为自动安装似乎有权限或环境问题）\n3. 或者尝试用另一种方法安装（比如使用chocolatey等包管理器）\n\n让我给用户一个清晰的回复。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，QQ安装遇到了一些问题。\n\n## 问题分析\n\n从日志来看，**QQ安装包下载成功了（188.31MB）**，但在启动安装程序时出错。错误信息显示无法启动安装进程，可能是因为：\n- 系统权限限制\n- 安全软件拦截\n- 或者需要用户手动确认安装\n\n## 建议解决方案\n\n**方案1：手动下载安装（推荐）**\n1. 打开浏览器访问 https://im.qq.com\n2. 点击\"立即下载\"下载QQ安装包\n3. 运行下载的安装程序，按提示完成安装\n\n**方案2：使用Microsoft Store**\n1. 打开Microsoft Store应用\n2. 搜索\"腾讯QQ\"或\"QQ\"\n3. 点击安装\n\n**方案3：我再尝试一次安装**\n如果你希望我再次尝试自动安装，我可以换一种方式重试。\n\n你希望选择哪种方案？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773510148106}}
